# Windsurf Rules — rare-rohit Monorepo
# Same rules as .cursorrules — kept in sync

## Stack
TypeScript 5 strict | React 18 | Vite 5 SWC | Tailwind v3 | Framer Motion v11
i18next bilingual (EN dev / HI prod) | React Router v6 | react-hook-form + zod

## Zero tolerance
- No .js/.jsx files — TypeScript only
- No `any` type — use `unknown` + guards
- No inline styles — Tailwind only (except motion transforms)
- No hardcoded strings — all via t() from react-i18next
- No hardcoded colors — Tailwind tokens only
- No default exports except App.tsx and page components

## Key conventions
- Aliases: @shared/ui | @shared/hooks | @shared/utils | @app/*
- Animation variants: always from @shared/utils/animations — never inline
- Cards dark bg: .card-divine | Cards light bg: .card-light
- Section layout: .section-padding + .section-container
- i18n: update en/ AND hi/ simultaneously
- Imports ordered: react → external → @shared/* → @app/* → relative

## Quality gate
npm run check → typecheck + lint + format:check — must pass before commit
